(firstQuint)The CLASP Study Edwards PASCAL TrAnScatheter Mitral Valve RePair System Study.

 The purpose of this study is to assess the safety, performance and clinical outcomes of the Edwards PASCAL Transcatheter Mitral Valve Repair (TMVr) System.

 This is a multi-center, multi-national, prospective, single arm, safety, performance and clinical outcomes study.

